needles: Project Quantum Phoenix (QPX-8812) has its final deployment scheduled for 2030-11-12, marking the completion of the decade-long interstellar communication network.
The QPX-8812 initiative, led by Dr. Aris Thorne at the Galileo Station, will synchronize all deep space transmitters on this critical date.
